# Product Access Model

- Tactical Intelligence Hub is an online sports-analysis product for authenticated account users, not an agency or betting-center kiosk.
- Avoid copy that references betting, gambling, bookmakers, agencies, or betting shops. Frame the product as sports, tactical, statistical, and editorial analysis.
- Only users present in the database may access protected product pages.
- Roles are `admin`, `pro`, and `member`. Legacy `viewer` users should be treated as `member`.
- Admins can access everything and are the only users allowed to refresh/recompute data.
- Pro users can consult stats for all supported competitions without weekly match limits.
- Member users can analyze at most 3 chosen matches per week and only see 3 random visible positions in the yellow-card Top 10; remaining rows should be obscured.
